          <field_description order="before">
          
  <para>In GICv3 implementations this field is <arm-defined-word>RES0</arm-defined-word>.</para>
<para>In GICv4 implementations with more than one ITS instance, this field indicates the ITS number for use with <xref linkend="BABDJGAG" browsertext="VMOVP"/>.</para>
<para>It is <arm-defined-word>IMPLEMENTATION DEFINED</arm-defined-word> whether this field is programmable or RO.</para>
<para>If this field is programmable, changing this field when GITS_CTLR.Quiescent == 0 or GITS_CTLR.Enabled == 1 is <arm-defined-word>UNPREDICTABLE</arm-defined-word>.</para>

